{"tid":1727434,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"本人特止聲明：唔會同任何一個為呢個運動付出既手足割蓆","createTime":"2019-11-16T12:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T06:33:05.000Z","uid":66483,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"26587201b9a00173906a3a3ef6fc27fcf940e8ea","tid":1727434,"uid":66483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"小弟情願割包皮<br />\n都唔會同各位相同理念既兄弟割蓆<br />\n雖然呢個星期真係送左好多子彈比對家，飲茶聽到好多師奶廢老轉風向<br />\n但呢個星期我地唔好再攪分化啦<br />\n<br />\n我地咁多位兄弟手足，盡力去做，各有各做，鋪天蓋地去做文宣表達我地根本係100%正確既理念，好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n還記得我地講好左：<br />\n<br />\n核爆都唔割蓆，和勇不割<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化<br />\n<br />\n我一直都期待同咁多位兄弟，起煲底除低口罩除低頭盔相擁，我連香檳都買埋，我真係好想同各位手足一齊建立新香港，我真係好想我地既下一代係有將來<br />\n<br />\n呢個星期我地一齊去做好自己咁先唔會辜負我地失去左既手足，好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n我好期待1124果日，我地可以用選票去令到林鄭 藍絲  建制 阿爺  廢老失望，我好奇待佢地失望個樣係點<br />\n<br />\n所以由今日起，應承我，我地要團結一致打我地目前為止可以打既仗，莫失莫忘呢五個月發生既事。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n1124 血責票償 香港人復仇！"},{"pid":"96d0b2b6bf6898391494e84ce0c11548b4a79728","tid":1727434,"uid":204916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:12:18.000Z","msg":"老虎蟹都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7b9a2416408912b84c3cd9b37cd02d74eda415","tid":1727434,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"何止不割<br />\n有咩事第一時間出黎護啊！"},{"pid":"87fc877d60ca080b48cb8cd41735c0c0ead4c626","tid":1727434,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:17:52.000Z","msg":"與其話同佢哋割<br />\n倒不如佢哋唔嫌細路我廢同我割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fef4aa6bc3aa3b1bd3b6f85f702208b11cc0cb5","tid":1727434,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:19:28.000Z","msg":"[文宣組入] 請唔好幫候選人做文宣！犯法仲會累人坐監！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728047/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728047/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"33d885202fea875011b90738d7b1faacea09156e","tid":1727434,"uid":246375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:24:29.000Z","msg":"唔割有做錯意味<br />\n要講就講永遠同前線手足同行<br />\n點都唔會被分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a8e2952766ff1547b80b540d1841c241bdd843","tid":1727434,"uid":66483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:11:11.000Z","msg":"勇武手足請受小弟一拜，有咩唔夠用既隨時同我講，我即刻科過黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：物資撚"},{"pid":"b9bae22f3693f4c3477a1cd53659588ec8173f3c","tid":1727434,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa52a5ce08af4e1c993149bd058c76c2117ba3f","tid":1727434,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:24:12.000Z","msg":"who are you?"},{"pid":"9db0c27dc71d97489361ae2a40be97b0065d7a31","tid":1727434,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:41:48.000Z","msg":"你老幾<br />\n做過d乜野幫呢場運動？"},{"pid":"c098441763e6f2f11c5d8c365afa2b65121c3714","tid":1727434,"uid":304160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同你想法一樣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我都求下前線唔好同我割呀 雖然我唔係前線 你每一位既付出 我真係唔知點去報搭 但一定會幫! 但願手足們平平安安 一世好人 煲底見</span>"},{"pid":"d751b8df396655ec05c316d09c74fdc84f546aa2","tid":1727434,"uid":66483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9db0c27dc71d97489361ae2a40be97b0065d7a31","tid":1727434,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T01:41:48.000Z","msg":"你老幾<br />\n做過d乜野幫呢場運動？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:29:48.00